'''Goodreads'''是一家图书分享型社交网站。网站由Otis Chandler和Elizabeth Chandler创立，于2006年底启动，2007年1月正式推出<ref name="Goodreads About us">{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/about/us |title=About Us |website=Goodreads |language=en |accessdate=2012-12-20 |archive-date=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208184439/https://www.goodreads.com/about/us |dead-url=no }}</ref>，总部位于美国[[旧金山|旧金山]]<ref>{{Citation |url=http://www.insidebayarea.com/news/ci_22954537/book-lovers-seething-over-amazon-acquisition-goodreads |newspaper=''Inside Bay Area'' |title=Book lovers seething over Amazon acquisition of Goodreads |language=en |accessdate=2014-03-15 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115049/http://www.insidebayarea.com/news/ci_22954537/book-lovers-seething-over-amazon-acquisition-goodreads |dead-url=no }}.</ref>。网站允许访客搜索网站内已收录的书目、注释和书评。注册用户可以添加新书目和推荐书单，也可以建立自己的图书讨论小组。但唯有Librarians以及雇員可以編輯修改書目資料，註冊用戶無此權限，必須向Goodreads官方申請資格，官方會審核用戶閱讀量及電子申請函核定是否成為Librarians，Librarians與雇員的其一相異處在於Librarians是志願服務不支薪，其權限可以變更書目資料、結合不同語言版本、合併重複書目和刪除部分書籍，Librarians不能更動的書目可提交Super Librarians支援編輯。Goodreads官方認為由Librarians來管理書目資料庫即可使得網站收藏量有秩序，並不開放所有用戶擁有編輯權。<ref name="Goodreads Librarian Manual">{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/librarian_manual |title=Librarian Manual |website=Goodreads |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-06 |archive-date=2019-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114220941/https://www.goodreads.com/librarian_manual |dead-url=no }}</ref>
到2007年12月为止，网站已有超过65万注册用户<ref>{{Citation |url=http://www.techcoastreview.com/2007/12/good-reads-book-nerds-social-networking.html |publisher=TechCoastReview |title=Good reads: book nerds social networking |language=en |accessdate=2007-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071219212812/http://www.techcoastreview.com/2007/12/good-reads-book-nerds-social-networking.html |archivedate=2007-12-19 }}.</ref>，所收录的书名总数超过了1千万。<ref name = TCAngel>{{cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2007/12/17/goodreads-raises-angel-round-to-help-you-find-that-perfect-book/#comment-1853293 |title=Goodreads Raises Angel Round To Help You Find That Perfect Book |publisher=Tech Crunch |language=en |accessdate=2012-10-22 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218035344/https://techcrunch.com/2007/12/17/goodreads-raises-angel-round-to-help-you-find-that-perfect-book/#comment-1853293 |dead-url=no }}</ref>到2012年7月，网站已有1千万注册用户，月访问量达到2千万，拥有雇员30人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/default/article/Goodreads-Otis-Chandler-reviews-growth-3725030.php |last=Lee |first=Ellen |title=Goodreads' Otis Chandler reviews growth |publisher=SF Gate |language=en |accessdate=2012-10-22 |archive-date=2013-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401084151/http://www.sfgate.com/default/article/Goodreads-Otis-Chandler-reviews-growth-3725030.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>到2013年6月23日，网站注册用户又翻了一倍，达到2千万。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/blog/show/425-goodreads-grows-to-20-million-readers |title=Goodreads Grows to 20 Million Readers |author=Otis Chandler |language=en |date=2013-07-23|accessdate=2014-03-15 |archive-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215001107/http://www.goodreads.com/blog/show/425-goodreads-grows-to-20-million-readers |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年3月28日，[[Amazon.com|亚马逊公司]]宣布买下Goodreads网站，但并未透露购买时所支付的具体金额。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/03/28/amazon-acquires-social-reading-site-goodreads/ |last=Olanoff |first=Drew |title=Amazon Acquires Social Reading Site Goodreads, Which Gives The Company A Social Advantage Over Apple |publisher=SF Gate |language=en |accessdate=2012-10-22 |archive-date=2020-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215065332/https://techcrunch.com/2013/03/28/amazon-acquires-social-reading-site-goodreads/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

